      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, has been maintained to an uncompromising standard. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of investment-grade quality, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. We invite discerning buyers to inspect this peerless example of automotive excellence.",
